    question: "What is full stomach waxing?",
    answer: "Full stomach waxing (also called full strip stomach wax) removes all hair from the entire stomach area, from just below the chest to the bikini line. This creates completely smooth skin across the midsection."
  },
  {
    question: "Does stomach waxing hurt?",
    answer: "Stomach waxing causes moderate discomfort, but most clients find it manageable. The stomach area is less sensitive than bikini areas, and the results are worth the brief discomfort."
  },
  {
    question: "How long does stomach waxing last?",
    answer: "Stomach waxing typically lasts 4-6 weeks. Results vary depending on individual hair growth cycles."
  }
];
